 sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWriting: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\t<a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/Pronto\" target=\"_blank\">Pronto</a><br />\n\tPronto is in informal way of indicating something has to be done immediately, quickly. What has to be done pronto? Why? What will be the outcome?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: They looked for it, pronto... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) making a turn, pronto<br />\n\t2) get the project done, pronto<br />\n\t3) went back home, pronto<br />\n\t4) deliver it, pronto<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tTaking utmost precaution, Doug kept his body low and slowly headed towards the department door. He could not wait any longer; he needed to get out of the area, pronto. Placing his ear against the heavy door, he tried to sense if there was any commotion at all on the other side. It just did not make sense. Why would someone scan a key card and walk away? Staring hard at the door, Doug adjusted the cap on his head, the limited edition designer cap with a pair of angle wing designs on either side.</p>\n<p>\n\